  59def read_schedules(connection, table="flight_schedule", subset_table="flight_subset",
  60	scenario_table="scenario", scenario=0, scenario_in_schedules=False):
  61	# Not: I am not using a "SELECT *" because there are several fields called
  62	# 'id', which need to be renamed
  63	# sql = "SELECt fs.nid as flight_id, fs.max_seats as max_seats, fs.aircraft_type as aircraft_type, \
  64	# 	fs.registration as registration, fs.sobt as sobt, fs.sibt as sibt, fs.origin as origin,\
  65	# 	fs.destination as destination, fs.\
  66
  67	if scenario_in_schedules:
  68		sql = "SELECt fs.*\
  69			FROM {} fs \
  70			WHERE fs.scenario_id = {}".format(table, scenario)
  71		
  72	else:
  73		sql = "SELECT IF( \
  74					(SELECt s.flight_set \
  75					FROM {} s \
  76					WHERE s.id = {}) IS NULL, \
  77					'YES', \
  78					'NO' \
  79					) as answer;".format(scenario_table, scenario)
  80
  81		subset_is_null = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)['answer'].iloc[0]
  82
  83		if subset_is_null == 'YES':
  84			sql = """SELECt fs.*
  85					FROM flight_schedule_old1409 fs"""
  86		elif subset_is_null=='NO':
  87			sql = "SELECt fs.* \
  88					FROM {} fs \
  89					JOIN {} fsb ON fsb.flight_id = fs.nid \
  90					JOIN {} s ON s.flight_set = fsb.subset \
  91					WHERE s.id = {}".format(table, subset_table, scenario_table, scenario)
  92		else:
  93			raise Exception('Subset of flight is null')
  94	
  95	d_schedules = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
  96
  97	return d_schedules

 100def read_iedf_atfm(connection, table="iedf_atfm_static", where=None, scipy_distr=False, scenario=None):
 101
 102	sql = "SELECt a.x, a.y FROM {} a ".format(table)
 103
 104	if where is not None:
 105		sql = sql + where
 106
 107	sql = sql + " ORDER BY a.index"
 108
 109	d_iedf = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
 110
 111	if not scipy_distr:
 112		x, y = d_iedf['x'], d_iedf['y']
 113		iedf = interp1d(x, y)
 114		return iedf
 115	else:
 116		y, x = d_iedf['x'], d_iedf['y']
 117		x = [0., 0.01, x[0]-0.01] + list(x)
 118		y = [y[0], y[0], y[0]] + list(y)
 119		yy = [y[0]] + [y[i+1]-y[i] for i in range(len(y)-1)]
 120		pdf = interp1d(x, yy)
 121		xx = np.linspace(min(x), max(x), 100)
 122
 123		hist_dist = stats.rv_histogram((pdf(xx)[:-1]/sum(pdf(xx)[:-1]), xx))
 124
 125		return hist_dist

 206def read_crco_charges(connection, crco_charges_table='crco_charges_static', crco_vat_table='crco_vat_static',
 207	crco_fix_table='crco_fix_static', crco_overfly_table='crco_overfly_static',crco_weight_table='crco_weight_static'):
 208	#Read CRCO charges info
 209	sql = "SELECt sid, unit_rate FROM " + crco_charges_table
 210	d_crco_charges = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
 211	
 212	sql = "SELECt sid, vat FROM " + crco_vat_table
 213	d_crco_vat = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
 214	
 215	sql = "SELECt sid, unit_rate FROM " + crco_fix_table
 216	d_crco_fix = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
 217	
 218	sql = "SELECt sid, unit_rate FROM " + crco_overfly_table
 219	d_crco_overfly = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
 220	
 221	sql = "SELECt sid, from_t, to_t, unit_rate FROM "+crco_weight_table
 222	d_crco_weight = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
 223	
 224
 225	#Add VAT
 226	d_crco_charges = pd.merge(d_crco_charges, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
 227	d_crco_charges.loc[d_crco_charges['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
 228	d_crco_fix = pd.merge(d_crco_fix, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
 229	d_crco_fix.loc[d_crco_fix['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
 230	d_crco_overfly = pd.merge(d_crco_overfly, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
 231	d_crco_overfly.loc[d_crco_overfly['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
 232	d_crco_weight = pd.merge(d_crco_weight, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
 233	d_crco_weight.loc[d_crco_weight['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
 234
 235	#Compute unit rate (t) with VAT
 236	d_crco_charges['t'] = round(d_crco_charges['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_charges['vat']/100))
 237	d_crco_overfly['t'] = round(d_crco_overfly['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_overfly['vat']/100))
 238	d_crco_fix['t'] = round(d_crco_fix['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_fix['vat']/100))
 239	d_crco_weight['t'] = round(d_crco_weight['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_weight['vat']/100))
 240	
 241	return d_crco_charges, d_crco_overfly, d_crco_fix, d_crco_weight

 243def read_fp_routes_without_crco(connection, fp_pool_table='fp_pool_m', fp_pool_point_table='fp_pool_point_m',
 244	trajectory_pool_table='trajectory_pool',trajectories_version=3):
 245	
 246	sql = "SELECt f.id, f.icao_orig, icao_dest, \
 247		IF(bada4_mtow.mtow is not null, bada4_mtow.mtow, amtow.mtow) AS mtow, \
 248		fp.sequence, fp.ansp, ST_X(fp.coords) AS lat, ST_Y(fp.coords) AS lon \
 249		FROM "+fp_pool_table+" f \
 250		JOIN "+fp_pool_point_table+" fp on fp.fp_pool_id=f.id \
 251		JOIN "+trajectory_pool_table+" tp on f.trajectory_pool_id=tp.id \
 252		LEFT JOIN (select bada_code_ac_model, mtow FROM ac_eq_badacomputed_static aebc \
 253		JOIN bada4_2.ac_models_selected a_m_s ON aebc.bada_code_ac_model=a_m_s.ac_model AND aebc.ac_icao=a_m_s.icao_model \
 254		JOIN ac_mtow_static amtow on amtow.ac=aebc.ac_icao) AS bada4_mtow ON bada4_mtow.bada_code_ac_model=f.bada_code_ac_model \
 255		LEFT JOIN ac_mtow_static amtow ON amtow.ac=f.bada_code_ac_model \
 256		WHERE f.crco_cost_EUR is NULL AND tp.version="+str(trajectories_version)+" \
 257		ORDER BY f.id, fp.sequence"
 258	fp_nas = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql)
 259	
 260	fp_nas['mtow'] = fp_nas['mtow']*1000
 261
 262	return fp_nas

 264def add_crco_to_flights_in_db(connection, d_crco, fp_pool_table='fp_pool_m',
 265	trajectory_pool_table='trajectory_pool',trajectories_version=3):
 266	
 267	connection['engine'].execute("DROP TABLE IF EXISTS crco_temp")
 268	
 269	d_crco[['id','crco_cost_EUR']].to_sql('crco_temp', connection['engine'])
 270
 271	sql = "UPDATe "+fp_pool_table+" f \
 272			JOIN "+trajectory_pool_table+" tp ON f.trajectory_pool_id=tp.id \
 273			JOIN crco_temp c ON c.id=f.id \
 274			SET f.crco_cost_EUR=c.crco_cost_EUR \
 275			WHERE tp.version="+str(trajectories_version)
 276
 277	connection['engine'].execute(sql)
 278
 279	connection['engine'].execute("DROP TABLE IF EXISTS crco_temp")

 282def read_airports_data(connection, airport_table="airport_info_static", taxi_in_table="taxi_in_static",
 283	taxi_out_table="taxi_out_static", airports=None, scenario=None):
 284
 285	sql = "SELECt a_s.icao_id, a_s.altitude, a_s.tis, a_s.trs, a_s.taxi_time, a_s.lat AS lat, a_s.lon AS lon, a_s.time_zone, \
 286			IF(t_o.mean_txo is not NULL, t_o.mean_txo, a_s.mean_taxi_out) as mean_taxi_out, \
 287			IF(t_o.std_deviation is not NULL, t_o.std_deviation, a_s.std_taxi_out) as std_taxi_out, \
 288			IF(t_i.mean_txi is not NULL, t_i.mean_txi, a_s.mean_taxi_in) as mean_taxi_in, \
 289			IF(t_i.std_deviation is not NULL, t_i.std_deviation, a_s.std_taxi_in) as std_taxi_in, \
 290			a_s.MCT_standard, a_s.MCT_domestic, a_s.MCT_international, \
 291			a_s.ECAC, a_s.atfm_area, a_s.nas, \
 292			a_s.declared_capacity, a_s.size \
 293			FROM {} a_s \
 294			LEFT JOIN {} t_i ON t_i.icao_id=a_s.icao_id \
 295			LEFT JOIN {} t_o on t_o.icao_id=a_s.icao_id".format(airport_table, taxi_in_table, taxi_out_table)
 296
 297	if airports is not None:
 298		sql = sql + " WHERE a_s.icao_id IN ("+str(airports)[1:-1]+")"
 299
 300	df = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
 301
 302	return df

 316def read_airports_curfew_data(connection, airport_table='airport_curfew', icao_airport_name='icao_id',
 317	curfew_airport_name='curfew', curfews_db_table=None, curfews_db_table2=None, airports=None,
 318	only_ECAC=True, airport_info_table='airport_info_static', curfew_extra_time_table=None, scenario=None):
 319
 320	sql = "SELECt c.{} as icao_id, c.{} as curfew ".format(icao_airport_name, curfew_airport_name)
 321
 322	if curfew_extra_time_table is not None:
 323		sql += ", extra_curfew"
 324	
 325	sql += " FROM {} c".format(airport_table)
 326
 327	if curfews_db_table is not None:
 328		sql += " JOIN {} cd on c.{}=cd.icao".format(curfews_db_table, icao_airport_name)
 329
 330	if curfews_db_table2 is not None:
 331		sql += " JOIN {} cd2 on c.{}=cd2.icao_id".format(curfews_db_table2, icao_airport_name)
 332
 333	if only_ECAC:
 334		sql += " JOIN {} ais on ais.icao_id=c.{}".format(airport_info_table, icao_airport_name)
 335
 336	if curfew_extra_time_table is not None:
 337		sql += " LEFT JOIN {} ec on ec.icao=c.{}".format(curfew_extra_time_table, icao_airport_name)
 338
 339	
 340	if (airports is not None) or (only_ECAC) or (curfews_db_table2 is not None):
 341		sql += " WHERE "
 342		if airports is not None:
 343			sql += " c."+icao_airport_name+" IN ("+str(airports)[1:-1]+") AND c."+curfew_airport_name+" is not NULL"
 344			if only_ECAC:
 345				sql += " AND ais.ECAC=1"
 346			if (curfews_db_table2 is not None):
 347				sql += " AND cd2.curfew is not NULL"
 348		elif only_ECAC:
 349			sql += " ais.ECAC=1"
 350			if (curfews_db_table2 is not None):
 351				sql += " AND cd2.curfew is not NULL"
 352		else:
 353			sql += " cd2.curfew is not NULL"
 354
 355	d_curfew = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
 356
 357	if len(d_curfew):
 358		d_curfew['curfew']=pd.to_timedelta(d_curfew['curfew'])
 359
 360		d_curfew.loc[np.isnat(d_curfew['curfew']),'curfew'] = -1
 361		d_curfew['curfew'] = d_curfew['curfew'].apply(lambda x: (dt.datetime.min + x).time() if not x is -1 else None)
 362
 363		def ceil_dt(t, res):
 364			# how many secs have passed this day
 365			nsecs = t.hour*3600 + t.minute*60 + t.second + t.microsecond*1e-6
 366			delta = res.seconds - nsecs % res.seconds
 367			if delta == res.seconds:
 368				delta = 0
 369			return t + dt.timedelta(seconds=delta)
 370
 371		if curfew_extra_time_table is not None:
 372			buffer_curfew = 15
 373			d_curfew.loc[~d_curfew['extra_curfew'].isnull(),'extra_curfew']=d_curfew.loc[~d_curfew['extra_curfew'].isnull(),'extra_curfew']+buffer_curfew
 374			d_curfew.loc[d_curfew['extra_curfew'].isnull(),'extra_curfew']=0
 375			d_curfew['curfew'] = d_curfew.apply(lambda x: (dt.datetime.combine(dt.date.today(), x['curfew'])+dt.timedelta(minutes=x['extra_curfew'])).time(),axis=1)
 376			d_curfew['curfew'] = d_curfew['curfew'].apply(lambda x: ceil_dt(dt.datetime.combine(dt.date.today(),x),dt.timedelta(minutes=15)).time())
 377
 378	return d_curfew

 490def read_coord_trajectory_route(connection, route_pool_table="route_pool",
 491	route_pool_has_airspace_table="route_pool_has_airspace_static",
 492	airspace_table="airspace_static", icao_orig=None, icao_dest=None, condition=None):
 493	
 494	sql = "SELECt coords.id, coords.icao_orig, coords.icao_dest, coords.lat, coords.lon, coords.distance as distance_km, coords.sid as nas, \
 495				 coords.point_type as entry_exit FROM \
 496		(select rps.id, rps.icao_orig, rps.icao_dest, \
 497		  ST_X(rpshas.entry_point) as lat, ST_Y(rpshas.entry_point) as lon, 'ENTRY' as point_type, a.sid, \
 498		  rpshas.distance_entry as distance \
 499		from "+route_pool_table+" rps \
 500		join "+route_pool_has_airspace_table+" rpshas on rpshas.route_pool_id=rps.id \
 501		join "+airspace_table+" a on a.id=rpshas.airspace_id "
 502
 503	if icao_orig is not None:
 504		sql += "where rps.icao_orig LIKE \""+icao_orig+"\" and rps.icao_dest LIKE \""+icao_dest+"\" "
 505
 506	elif condition is not None:
 507		sql += "where "+condition
 508
 509	sql += "UNION \
 510		select rps.id, rps.icao_orig, rps.icao_dest, \
 511		ST_X(rpshas.exit_point) as lat, ST_Y(rpshas.exit_point) as lon, 'EXIT' as point_type, \
 512		a.sid, rpshas.distance_exit as distance \
 513		from "+route_pool_table+" rps \
 514		join "+route_pool_has_airspace_table+" rpshas on rpshas.route_pool_id=rps.id \
 515		join "+airspace_table+" a on a.id=rpshas.airspace_id "
 516
 517	if icao_orig is not None:
 518		sql += "where rps.icao_orig LIKE \""+icao_orig+"\" and rps.icao_dest LIKE \""+icao_dest+"\""
 519	elif condition is not None:
 520		sql += "where "+condition
 521
 522	sql += ") as coords \
 523		order by coords.id, coords.distance, coords.point_type ASC"
 524
 525
 526	#print(sql)
 527	d_coords = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql)
 528	
 529	#d_coords = read_mysql(query=sql, engine=engine)
 530
 531	d_coords.loc[d_coords['entry_exit']=="EXIT",'nas']=None
 532
 533	d_coords.fillna(method='ffill', inplace=True)
 534
 535	d_coords.drop(columns=['entry_exit'], inplace=True)
 536
 537	d_coords = d_coords.drop_duplicates()
 538
 539	return d_coords

 542def read_trajectories_missing_in_interval(connection, flight_schedule_table="flight_schedule", subset_table="flight_subset", 
 543	ac_eq_badacomputed_static_table="ac_eq_badacomputed_static", route_pool_table="route_pool",
 544	trajectory_pool_table="trajectory_pool", scenario=0, trajectories_version=0, minimum_trajectory=0,
 545	maximum_trajectory=None, number_trajectories=None, scenario_in_schedules=False):
 546
 547	if scenario_in_schedules:
 548		sql = "SELECt DISTINCT rp.id as route_pool_id, rp.icao_orig, rp.icao_dest, aebs.bada_code_ac_model, rp.fp_distance_km \
 549				IF(tp.route_pool_id	is NULL, 0, 1) as computed \
 550				FROM "+flight_schedule_table+" fs \
 551				JOIN "+ac_eq_badacomputed_static_table+" aebs ON aebs.ac_icao = fs.aircraft_type \
 552				JOIN "+route_pool_table+" rp ON rp.icao_orig = fs.origin and rp.icao_dest = fs.destination \
 553				LEFT JOIN (SELECT tp.route_pool_id, tp.bada_code_ac_model FROM "+trajectory_pool_table+" tp \
 554				WHERE tp.version = "+str(trajectories_version)+") AS tp ON tp.route_pool_id = rp.id AND tp.bada_code_ac_model = aebs.bada_code_ac_model \
 555				WHERE fs.scenario_id  = "+str(scenario)+" ORDER BY rp.fp_distance_km, aebs.bada_code_ac_model"
 556	else:
 557		#Schedules to use defined in subset table
 558		sql = "SELECt DISTINCT rp.id as route_pool_id, rp.icao_orig, rp.icao_dest, aebs.bada_code_ac_model, rp.fp_distance_km, \
 559				IF(tp.route_pool_id	is NULL, 0, 1) as computed \
 560				FROM scenario s \
 561				JOIN "+subset_table+" fsb ON fsb.subset = s.flight_set \
 562				JOIN "+flight_schedule_table+" fs ON fs.nid=fsb.flight_id \
 563				JOIN "+ac_eq_badacomputed_static_table+" aebs ON aebs.ac_icao = fs.aircraft_type \
 564				JOIN "+route_pool_table+" rp ON rp.icao_orig = fs.origin and rp.icao_dest = fs.destination \
 565				LEFT JOIN (SELECT tp.route_pool_id, tp.bada_code_ac_model FROM "+trajectory_pool_table+" tp \
 566				WHERE tp.version = "+str(trajectories_version)+") AS tp ON tp.route_pool_id = rp.id AND tp.bada_code_ac_model = aebs.bada_code_ac_model \
 567				WHERE s.id = "+str(scenario)+" ORDER BY rp.fp_distance_km, aebs.bada_code_ac_model"
 568
 569	df_traj = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql)
 570	df_traj['number']=df_traj.index
 571
 572	if maximum_trajectory is None:
 573		maximum_trajectory = len(df_traj)
 574
 575	trajectories_missing = df_traj.loc[(df_traj['number']>=minimum_trajectory) & (df_traj['number']<=maximum_trajectory)]
 576
 577	trajectories_missing = trajectories_missing.loc[trajectories_missing['computed']==0].reset_index(drop=True)
 578
 579	if number_trajectories is not None:
 580		trajectories_missing = trajectories_missing.iloc[0:number_trajectories]
 581
 582	return trajectories_missing

 671def read_trajectories_pool(connection, scenario, trajectories_version, trajectory_pool_table='trajectory_pool', trajectory_segments_table='trajectory_segment',
 672	route_pool_table='route_pool', flight_schedule_table='flight_schedule', flight_subset_table='flight_subset', scenario_table='scenario',
 673	scenario_in_schedules=False):
 674
 675	if scenario_in_schedules:
 676		sql = "SELECt DISTINCT fs.origin, fs.destination, tp.route_pool_id, tp.distance_orig_fp_km, tp.bada_code_ac_model, \
 677			tp.bada_version, tp.status as trajectory_status, ts.* \
 678			FROM "+trajectory_pool_table+" tp \
 679			JOIN "+trajectory_segments_table+" ts ON ts.trajectory_pool_id = tp.id \
 680			JOIN "+route_pool_table+" rp ON rp.id=tp.route_pool_id \
 681			JOIN "+flight_schedule_table+" fs ON rp.icao_orig = fs.origin and rp.icao_dest = fs.destination \
 682			WHERE tp.version="+str(trajectories_version)+" AND fs.scenario_id="+str(scenario)+" \
 683			ORDER by ts.trajectory_pool_id, ts.`order`"
 684
 685	else:
 686		sql = "SELECt DISTINCT fs.origin, fs.destination, tp.route_pool_id, tp.distance_orig_fp_km, tp.bada_code_ac_model, \
 687			tp.bada_version, tp.status as trajectory_status, ts.* \
 688			FROM "+trajectory_pool_table+" tp \
 689			JOIN "+trajectory_segments_table+" ts ON ts.trajectory_pool_id = tp.id \
 690			JOIN "+route_pool_table+" rp ON rp.id=tp.route_pool_id \
 691			JOIN "+flight_schedule_table+" fs ON rp.icao_orig = fs.origin and rp.icao_dest = fs.destination \
 692			JOIN "+flight_subset_table+" fsb ON fsb.flight_id = fs.nid \
 693			JOIN "+scenario_table+" s ON s.flight_set = fsb.subset \
 694			WHERE tp.version="+str(trajectories_version)+" AND s.id="+str(scenario)+" \
 695			ORDER by ts.trajectory_pool_id, ts.`order`"
 696
 697	df = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql)
 698
 699	df['avg_wind'] = df['avg_wind'].apply(lambda x: 0 if np.isnan(x) else x)
 700	df.loc[0, :] = len(df.columns) * [10]
 701	df['trajectory_segment'] = df.apply(lambda x: TrajectorySegment(x['fl_0'],x['fl_1'],x['distance_nm'],
 702																	x['time_min'],x['fuel_kg'],x['weight_0'],x['weight_1'],
 703																	x['segment_type'],x['avg_wind']), axis=1)
 704
 705	#raise Exception()
 706	dict_trajectories_pool = {}
 707	for origin, destination, route_pool_id, distance_orig_fp_km, bada_code_ac_model, bada_version, \
 708		trajectory_pool_id, order, trajectory_segment, status, trajectory_status in \
 709			 zip(df.origin, df.destination, df.route_pool_id, df.distance_orig_fp_km, df.bada_code_ac_model, df.bada_version, \
 710				df.trajectory_pool_id, df.order, df.trajectory_segment, df.status, df.trajectory_status): 
 711
 712
 713		#Check if we have already an option between the origin-destination-ac_icao
 714		trajectories_options = dict_trajectories_pool.get((origin, destination, bada_code_ac_model))
 715		if trajectories_options is None:
 716			#If not the create a dictionary to store the options for that o-d-ac
 717			trajectories_options = {}
 718			dict_trajectories_pool[(origin, destination, bada_code_ac_model)]=trajectories_options
 719
 720		#Check if we have a trajectory for this route-pool
 721		trajectory = trajectories_options.get(route_pool_id)
 722		if trajectory is None:
 723			#If not exists create the trajectory
 724			trajectory = Trajectory(ac_icao=None, ac_model=bada_code_ac_model, bada_version=bada_version, distance_orig_fp=distance_orig_fp_km/uc.nm2km) #We are missing oew, and mpl
 725			trajectory.status = trajectory_status
 726			trajectory.trajectory_pool_id = trajectory_pool_id
 727			trajectory.route_pool_id = route_pool_id
 728			trajectories_options[route_pool_id] = trajectory
 729
 730		
 731		trajectory_segment.status = status
 732
 733		trajectory.add_back_trajectory_segment(trajectory_segment)
 734
 735
 736	#for k in dict_trajectories_pool.keys():
 737	#	dict_trajectories_pool[k]=list(dict_trajectories_pool[k].values())
 738
 739	return dict_trajectories_pool

 783		sql += "FROM {} fp \
 784				JOIN {} fpp on fpp.fp_pool_id=fp.id \
 785				JOIN {} tp on tp.id = fp.trajectory_pool_id \
 786				JOIN (select distinct fs.origin, fs.destination \
 787				FROM {} fs \
 788				JOIN {} fsb ON fsb.flight_id = fs.nid \
 789				JOIN {} s ON s.flight_set = fsb.subset \
 790				WHERE s.id = {}) as origin_dest on origin_dest.origin=fp.icao_orig and origin_dest.destination=fp.icao_dest \
 791				WHERE tp.version = {} \
 792				ORDER BY fp.id, fpp.sequence;".format(fp_pool_table,
 793													  fp_pool_point_table,
 794													  trajectory_pool_table,
 795													  flight_schedule_table,
 796													  flight_subset_table,
 797													  scenario_table,
 798													  scenario,
 799													  trajectories_version)
 800		
 801	df = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
 802
 803	columns = set(df.columns)
 804	columns.add("planned_avg_speed_kt")
 805	columns.add("min_speed_kt")
 806	columns.add("max_speed_kt")
 807	columns.add("mrc_speed_kt")
 808
 809	df = df.reindex(columns = list(columns))      
 810
 811	df = df.replace({np.nan: None})

 861		"""

 864			act.wake, UPPER(act.engine_type) as engine_type \

 912																  x['ICAO_model'],
 913																  x['WTC'],x['S'],x['wref'],x['mnom'],x['mtow'],

 917																  [x['cf1'],x['cf2'],x['cfcr']],
 918																  x['clbo_mo'],x['k']), axis=1)
 919
 920		dict_perf = d_performance.set_index(dict_key).to_dict()['ac_perf']
 921
 922		d_performance.loc[d_performance['EngineType']=="Turboprop",'ac_perf']=d_performance[d_performance['EngineType']=="Turboprop"].apply(lambda x: bap.AircraftPerformanceBada3TP(
 923																	  x['ICAO_model'],
 924																	  x['WTC'],x['S'],x['wref'],x['mnom'],x['mtow'],
 925																	  x['oew'],x['mpl'],x['hmo'],x['vfe'],
 926																	  x['m_max'],x['v_stall'],
 927																	  [x['cd0'],x['cd2'],x['cm16']],
 928																	  [x['cf1'],x['cf2'],x['cfcr']],
 929																	  x['clbo_mo'],x['k']), axis=1)

 937		sql = "SELECt ptf.bada_code as ICAO_model, ptf.FL as fl, \

 988			dd['gamma']=(dd['rocd']*uc.f2m/60)/(dd['tas']/uc.ms2kt)
 989			dd['gamma']=dd['gamma'].apply(asin)
 990			dd['gamma']=dd['gamma']*(-180)/pi

 992			dict_perf.get(i).set_descent_fuel_flow_detailled_rate_performances(cdp[:,0],cdp[:,1],cdp[:,2],

 995
 996		sql = "select pto.bada_code as ICAO_model, pto.FL as fl, pto.Cruise_TAS as TAS, pai.mass_nom as mass \
 997				FROM {} pto \
 998				JOIN {} pai ON pai.bada_code=pto.bada_code \
 999				JOIN {} aat ON aat.bada_code=pto.bada_code \
1000				WHERE aat.engine_type<>\'Piston\' \
1001				AND pto.Cruise_TAS is not null".format(self.combine_db_table('ptf_operations'),
1002													   self.combine_db_table('ptf_ac_info'),
1003													   self.combine_db_table('apof_ac_type'))

1006		d_mach_selected['m'] = d_mach_selected[['TAS','fl']].apply(lambda x: uc.kt2m(x['TAS'],x['fl']), axis=1)
1007		dms = d_mach_selected.set_index(dict_key)
1008
1009		for i in dms.index.unique():
1010			cms = dms.loc[i,['fl','mass','m']].values
1011			dict_perf.get(i).set_detailled_mach_nominal(cms[:,0],cms[:,1],cms[:,2])
1012
1013		return dict_perf

1346#Flight uncertainties
1347def read_flight_uncertainty(connection, table='flight_uncertainties_static', phase='climb', scenario=None):
1348	sql = "SELECT mu, sigma, computed_as_crossing_fl FROM {} WHERE phase=\'{}\'".format(table, phase)
1349	
1350	d_row = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
1351
1352	row = d_row.iloc[0, :]
1353
1354	mu, sig, fl_crossing = row['mu'], row['sigma'], row['computed_as_crossing_fl']
1355
1356	dist = stats.norm(loc=mu, scale=sig)
1357
1358	return {'dist': dist, 'fl_crossing': fl_crossing}

1380		sql += " AND n_iter="+str(n_iter)

1385

1636def read_orig_destination_via_intermediate_shortest(engine, icao_orig, icao_dest, route_pool_table="route_pool_static"):
1637	sql ="Select fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest as icao_inter, fs2.icao_dest, \
1638		(fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) as total_fp_dist_km \
1639		from "+route_pool_table+" fs1 \
1640		join "+route_pool_table+" fs2 on fs2.icao_orig=fs1.icao_dest \
1641		join ( \
1642		select fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest as icao_inter, fs2.icao_dest, \
1643		max(fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) as max_total_fp_dist_km \
1644		from "+route_pool_table+" fs1 \
1645		join "+route_pool_table+" fs2 on fs2.icao_orig=fs1.icao_dest \
1646		join (select fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest as icao_inter, fs2.icao_dest \
1647		  from "+route_pool_table+" fs1 \
1648		  join "+route_pool_table+" fs2 on fs2.icao_orig=fs1.icao_dest \
1649		  where fs1.icao_orig=\""+icao_orig+"\" and fs2.icao_dest=\""+icao_dest+"\" \
1650		  order by (fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) ASC limit 1) as sortest_inter \
1651				  on sortest_inter.icao_orig=fs1.icao_orig and \
1652					  sortest_inter.icao_inter=fs1.icao_dest and \
1653					  sortest_inter.icao_dest=fs2.icao_dest \
1654		group by fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest, fs2.icao_dest) as max_dist_sortest_inter \
1655		  on max_dist_sortest_inter.icao_orig=fs1.icao_orig and \
1656			  max_dist_sortest_inter.icao_dest=fs2.icao_dest and \
1657			  max_dist_sortest_inter.max_total_fp_dist_km >= (fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) \
1658		where fs1.icao_orig=\""+icao_orig+"\" and fs2.icao_dest=\""+icao_dest+"\""
1659
1660	d_od_inter = read_mysql(query=sql, engine=engine)
1661
1662	return d_od_inter

1664def read_trajectories(engine, condition_trajectory_id=None):
1665	dt = read_trajectories_dataframe(engine, condition_trajectory_id)
1666
1667	trajectories={}
1668	for tid in dt['trajectory_id'].unique():
1669
1670		dt_t = dt.loc[dt['trajectory_id']==tid, ['ac_icao','ac_model','bada_version','fp_distance','fp_distance_orig','fp_time','fp_fuel',
1671										 'fp_weight_0','fp_weight_1','oew','mpl','pl','pl_perc','fp_fl_0','fp_fl_1','fp_fl_max',
1672										 'fp_status']].copy().drop_duplicates().reset_index(drop=True)
1673
1674		t=Trajectory(dt_t.loc[0,'ac_icao'],dt_t.loc[0,'ac_model'],dt_t.loc[0,'bada_version'],dt_t.loc[0,'oew'],dt_t.loc[0,'mpl'],
1675					dt_t.loc[0,'fp_distance_orig'])
1676
1677		t.status = dt_t.loc[0,'fp_status']
1678
1679		dt_ts = dt.loc[dt['trajectory_id']==tid, ['segment_order', 'segment_type', 'segment_distance',
1680				'segment_time', 'segment_fuel', 'segment_weight_0', 'segment_weight_1',
1681				'segment_fl_0', 'segment_fl_1', 'segment_avg_m', 'segment_status']].copy().reset_index(drop=True)
1682
1683
1684		for i in dt_ts.index:
1685			ts = t.trajectory_segment(dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_fl_0'],dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_fl_1'],dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_distance'],
1686									   dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_time'],dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_fuel'],dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_weight_0'],
1687									   dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_weight_1'],dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_type'])
1688
1689			ts.status = dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_status']
1690			ts.avg_m = dt_ts.loc[i,'segment_avg_m']
1691			t.add_back_trajectory_segment(ts)
1692			
1693			trajectories[tid] = t
1694
1695	return trajectories

def read_iedf_atfm( connection, table='iedf_atfm_static', where=None, scipy_distr=False, scenario=None): 
101def read_iedf_atfm(connection, table="iedf_atfm_static", where=None, scipy_distr=False, scenario=None):
102
103	sql = "SELECt a.x, a.y FROM {} a ".format(table)
104
105	if where is not None:
106		sql = sql + where
107
108	sql = sql + " ORDER BY a.index"
109
110	d_iedf = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
111
112	if not scipy_distr:
113		x, y = d_iedf['x'], d_iedf['y']
114		iedf = interp1d(x, y)
115		return iedf
116	else:
117		y, x = d_iedf['x'], d_iedf['y']
118		x = [0., 0.01, x[0]-0.01] + list(x)
119		y = [y[0], y[0], y[0]] + list(y)
120		yy = [y[0]] + [y[i+1]-y[i] for i in range(len(y)-1)]
121		pdf = interp1d(x, yy)
122		xx = np.linspace(min(x), max(x), 100)
123
124		hist_dist = stats.rv_histogram((pdf(xx)[:-1]/sum(pdf(xx)[:-1]), xx))
125
126		return hist_dist

def read_crco_charges( connection, crco_charges_table='crco_charges_static', crco_vat_table='crco_vat_static', crco_fix_table='crco_fix_static', crco_overfly_table='crco_overfly_static', crco_weight_table='crco_weight_static'): 
207def read_crco_charges(connection, crco_charges_table='crco_charges_static', crco_vat_table='crco_vat_static',
208	crco_fix_table='crco_fix_static', crco_overfly_table='crco_overfly_static',crco_weight_table='crco_weight_static'):
209	#Read CRCO charges info
210	sql = "SELECt sid, unit_rate FROM " + crco_charges_table
211	d_crco_charges = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
212	
213	sql = "SELECt sid, vat FROM " + crco_vat_table
214	d_crco_vat = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
215	
216	sql = "SELECt sid, unit_rate FROM " + crco_fix_table
217	d_crco_fix = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
218	
219	sql = "SELECt sid, unit_rate FROM " + crco_overfly_table
220	d_crco_overfly = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
221	
222	sql = "SELECt sid, from_t, to_t, unit_rate FROM "+crco_weight_table
223	d_crco_weight = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql).rename(columns={'sid':'nas_sid'})
224	
225
226	#Add VAT
227	d_crco_charges = pd.merge(d_crco_charges, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
228	d_crco_charges.loc[d_crco_charges['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
229	d_crco_fix = pd.merge(d_crco_fix, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
230	d_crco_fix.loc[d_crco_fix['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
231	d_crco_overfly = pd.merge(d_crco_overfly, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
232	d_crco_overfly.loc[d_crco_overfly['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
233	d_crco_weight = pd.merge(d_crco_weight, d_crco_vat[['nas_sid','vat']], on="nas_sid", how="left", suffixes=('','_vat'))
234	d_crco_weight.loc[d_crco_weight['vat'].isnull(),'vat']=0
235
236	#Compute unit rate (t) with VAT
237	d_crco_charges['t'] = round(d_crco_charges['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_charges['vat']/100))
238	d_crco_overfly['t'] = round(d_crco_overfly['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_overfly['vat']/100))
239	d_crco_fix['t'] = round(d_crco_fix['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_fix['vat']/100))
240	d_crco_weight['t'] = round(d_crco_weight['unit_rate'] * (1+d_crco_weight['vat']/100))
241	
242	return d_crco_charges, d_crco_overfly, d_crco_fix, d_crco_weight

def read_airports_curfew_data( connection, airport_table='airport_curfew', icao_airport_name='icao_id', curfew_airport_name='curfew', curfews_db_table=None, curfews_db_table2=None, airports=None, only_ECAC=True, airport_info_table='airport_info_static', curfew_extra_time_table=None, scenario=None): 
317def read_airports_curfew_data(connection, airport_table='airport_curfew', icao_airport_name='icao_id',
318	curfew_airport_name='curfew', curfews_db_table=None, curfews_db_table2=None, airports=None,
319	only_ECAC=True, airport_info_table='airport_info_static', curfew_extra_time_table=None, scenario=None):
320
321	sql = "SELECt c.{} as icao_id, c.{} as curfew ".format(icao_airport_name, curfew_airport_name)
322
323	if curfew_extra_time_table is not None:
324		sql += ", extra_curfew"
325	
326	sql += " FROM {} c".format(airport_table)
327
328	if curfews_db_table is not None:
329		sql += " JOIN {} cd on c.{}=cd.icao".format(curfews_db_table, icao_airport_name)
330
331	if curfews_db_table2 is not None:
332		sql += " JOIN {} cd2 on c.{}=cd2.icao_id".format(curfews_db_table2, icao_airport_name)
333
334	if only_ECAC:
335		sql += " JOIN {} ais on ais.icao_id=c.{}".format(airport_info_table, icao_airport_name)
336
337	if curfew_extra_time_table is not None:
338		sql += " LEFT JOIN {} ec on ec.icao=c.{}".format(curfew_extra_time_table, icao_airport_name)
339
340	
341	if (airports is not None) or (only_ECAC) or (curfews_db_table2 is not None):
342		sql += " WHERE "
343		if airports is not None:
344			sql += " c."+icao_airport_name+" IN ("+str(airports)[1:-1]+") AND c."+curfew_airport_name+" is not NULL"
345			if only_ECAC:
346				sql += " AND ais.ECAC=1"
347			if (curfews_db_table2 is not None):
348				sql += " AND cd2.curfew is not NULL"
349		elif only_ECAC:
350			sql += " ais.ECAC=1"
351			if (curfews_db_table2 is not None):
352				sql += " AND cd2.curfew is not NULL"
353		else:
354			sql += " cd2.curfew is not NULL"
355
356	d_curfew = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
357
358	if len(d_curfew):
359		d_curfew['curfew']=pd.to_timedelta(d_curfew['curfew'])
360
361		d_curfew.loc[np.isnat(d_curfew['curfew']),'curfew'] = -1
362		d_curfew['curfew'] = d_curfew['curfew'].apply(lambda x: (dt.datetime.min + x).time() if not x is -1 else None)
363
364		def ceil_dt(t, res):
365			# how many secs have passed this day
366			nsecs = t.hour*3600 + t.minute*60 + t.second + t.microsecond*1e-6
367			delta = res.seconds - nsecs % res.seconds
368			if delta == res.seconds:
369				delta = 0
370			return t + dt.timedelta(seconds=delta)
371
372		if curfew_extra_time_table is not None:
373			buffer_curfew = 15
374			d_curfew.loc[~d_curfew['extra_curfew'].isnull(),'extra_curfew']=d_curfew.loc[~d_curfew['extra_curfew'].isnull(),'extra_curfew']+buffer_curfew
375			d_curfew.loc[d_curfew['extra_curfew'].isnull(),'extra_curfew']=0
376			d_curfew['curfew'] = d_curfew.apply(lambda x: (dt.datetime.combine(dt.date.today(), x['curfew'])+dt.timedelta(minutes=x['extra_curfew'])).time(),axis=1)
377			d_curfew['curfew'] = d_curfew['curfew'].apply(lambda x: ceil_dt(dt.datetime.combine(dt.date.today(),x),dt.timedelta(minutes=15)).time())
378
379	return d_curfew

543def read_trajectories_missing_in_interval(connection, flight_schedule_table="flight_schedule", subset_table="flight_subset", 
544	ac_eq_badacomputed_static_table="ac_eq_badacomputed_static", route_pool_table="route_pool",
545	trajectory_pool_table="trajectory_pool", scenario=0, trajectories_version=0, minimum_trajectory=0,
546	maximum_trajectory=None, number_trajectories=None, scenario_in_schedules=False):
547
548	if scenario_in_schedules:
549		sql = "SELECt DISTINCT rp.id as route_pool_id, rp.icao_orig, rp.icao_dest, aebs.bada_code_ac_model, rp.fp_distance_km \
550				IF(tp.route_pool_id	is NULL, 0, 1) as computed \

557	else:
558		#Schedules to use defined in subset table
559		sql = "SELECt DISTINCT rp.id as route_pool_id, rp.icao_orig, rp.icao_dest, aebs.bada_code_ac_model, rp.fp_distance_km, \
560				IF(tp.route_pool_id	is NULL, 0, 1) as computed \

564				JOIN "+ac_eq_badacomputed_static_table+" aebs ON aebs.ac_icao = fs.aircraft_type \

567				WHERE tp.version = "+str(trajectories_version)+") AS tp ON tp.route_pool_id = rp.id AND tp.bada_code_ac_model = aebs.bada_code_ac_model \
568				WHERE s.id = "+str(scenario)+" ORDER BY rp.fp_distance_km, aebs.bada_code_ac_model"
569
570	df_traj = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql)
571	df_traj['number']=df_traj.index
572
573	if maximum_trajectory is None:
574		maximum_trajectory = len(df_traj)
575
576	trajectories_missing = df_traj.loc[(df_traj['number']>=minimum_trajectory) & (df_traj['number']<=maximum_trajectory)]
577

579
580	if number_trajectories is not None:
581		trajectories_missing = trajectories_missing.iloc[0:number_trajectories]
582
583	return trajectories_missing

 847		self.db_in_parquet = type(self.db) == type(Path())

 849	def combine_db_table(self, table_name):
 850		if self.db_in_parquet:
 851			return self.db / Path(table_name)
 852		else:
 853			return '{}.{}'.format(self.db, Path(table_name))

 857		Reads BADA3 list of ac types and create a dictionary with synonims ac according to BADA3
 858		and which is their wake and engine type.
 859
 860		In BADA3 aircraft are identified by bada_code.

 862		"""

1348def read_flight_uncertainty(connection, table='flight_uncertainties_static', phase='climb', scenario=None):
1349	sql = "SELECT mu, sigma, computed_as_crossing_fl FROM {} WHERE phase=\'{}\'".format(table, phase)
1350	
1351	d_row = read_data(connection=connection, query=sql, scenario=scenario)
1352
1353	row = d_row.iloc[0, :]
1354
1355	mu, sig, fl_crossing = row['mu'], row['sigma'], row['computed_as_crossing_fl']
1356
1357	dist = stats.norm(loc=mu, scale=sig)
1358
1359	return {'dist': dist, 'fl_crossing': fl_crossing}

def read_orig_destination_via_intermediate_shortest(engine, icao_orig, icao_dest, route_pool_table='route_pool_static'): 
1637def read_orig_destination_via_intermediate_shortest(engine, icao_orig, icao_dest, route_pool_table="route_pool_static"):
1638	sql ="Select fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest as icao_inter, fs2.icao_dest, \
1639		(fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) as total_fp_dist_km \
1640		from "+route_pool_table+" fs1 \
1641		join "+route_pool_table+" fs2 on fs2.icao_orig=fs1.icao_dest \
1642		join ( \
1643		select fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest as icao_inter, fs2.icao_dest, \
1644		max(fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) as max_total_fp_dist_km \
1645		from "+route_pool_table+" fs1 \
1646		join "+route_pool_table+" fs2 on fs2.icao_orig=fs1.icao_dest \
1647		join (select fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest as icao_inter, fs2.icao_dest \
1648		  from "+route_pool_table+" fs1 \
1649		  join "+route_pool_table+" fs2 on fs2.icao_orig=fs1.icao_dest \
1650		  where fs1.icao_orig=\""+icao_orig+"\" and fs2.icao_dest=\""+icao_dest+"\" \
1651		  order by (fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) ASC limit 1) as sortest_inter \
1652				  on sortest_inter.icao_orig=fs1.icao_orig and \
1653					  sortest_inter.icao_inter=fs1.icao_dest and \
1654					  sortest_inter.icao_dest=fs2.icao_dest \
1655		group by fs1.icao_orig, fs1.icao_dest, fs2.icao_dest) as max_dist_sortest_inter \
1656		  on max_dist_sortest_inter.icao_orig=fs1.icao_orig and \
1657			  max_dist_sortest_inter.icao_dest=fs2.icao_dest and \
1658			  max_dist_sortest_inter.max_total_fp_dist_km >= (fs1.fp_distance_km + fs2.fp_distance_km) \
1659		where fs1.icao_orig=\""+icao_orig+"\" and fs2.icao_dest=\""+icao_dest+"\""
1660
1661	d_od_inter = read_mysql(query=sql, engine=engine)
1662
1663	return d_od_inter
